requirements:
- nothing can`t be lost
- publish/subscribe == kafka
- at least once delivery == syncronous write/read(do not move offset until all customers read)
- read once more for several days (timestamp)
- schemas on events
- dirrenet data centers

schema:
services - API - service data-bus - storage 

- KAFKA as storage => service data bus
- methods: produce/consume, offset (oldest, newest, timestamp)
- http/rpc => statefull
- websocket => stateless, one connect per clien/service